    "title" : "Mapstruct @named function with partial arguments",
    "body" : "<p>I want map 1 field using several arguments, but not all arguments, for example:</p>\n<pre><code>@Mapping(target = &quot;ss&quot;, source = &quot;.&quot;, qualifiedByName = &quot;sumThree&quot;)\nTrgt map(int a, int b, int c, int x, int y, int z); \n@Named(&quot;sumThree&quot;)\n static int sum(int a, int b, int c) {\n    return a + b + c;\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>Is it possible?</p>\n",
